Package: tidymine
Type: Package
Title: Tidy interface for calculating Maximal Information-based Nonparametric Exploration (MINE) statistics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Jobi", "Kroese", email = "joe@citizense.org",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: tidymine provides a tidy interface for calculating statistics from the Maximal Information-based Nonparametric Exploration (MINE) family.
    MINE provides a robust alternative to correlation measures, recognising a range of functional and non-functional relationships between variables.
